## Technologies Used

- AWS
- Terraform
- GitHub Actions
- OIDC Federation
- VPC
- EC2
- Infrastructure as Code (IaC)

---

## CI/CD Pipeline

This project uses GitHub Actions to automate Terraform workflows including:

- Terraform validation
- Terraform plan
- Terraform apply
- Terraform destroy workflows
- Secure AWS authentication using OIDC

---

## Security Best Practices

- No long-term AWS access keys
- OIDC-based authentication
- Modular infrastructure deployment
- Terraform state management
- Infrastructure version control

